Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.map

All map related functionality.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BaseMapElement Half of a map, represents an object that has been mapped to or from.
CloneMapping Deprecated.  
CSVParser An interface that provides access to CSV files.
Map The Map interface that basically represents a relationship between two BaseMapElements (or MetaObjects).
Mapping The primary interface which contains all Mapping information.
ObjectParser Future release : An interface that provides access to external object graphs.
View Interface for graphical view information.
 

Class Summary
HL7V3DataResult This class contains the generated the list of HL7 V3 data and the corresponding validation results.
MapBuilderImpl Builder of map files.
MapParserImpl Parser of map files.
MappingResult Contains mapping information and validation results.
MapProcessorHelper This class assists the MapProcessor with alot of the buisness logic.
MapProcessorImpl Processor of map files.
MapReportGenerator This class defines functions to generate a basic map report in Excel format.
RimGraphGen Generate Rim Objects from HL7 V3(HSM) Data Objects.
RimGraphResult This class contains a HL7 V3 Rim Object and corresponding validation results.
TransformationResult This class contains the generated HL7 V3 message text and corresponding validation results.
TransformationService By given csv file and mapping file, call generate method which will return the list of TransformationResult.
 

Exception Summary
MappingException An exception for the mapping subsystem.
 

Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.map Description

All map related functionality.
